These were some of the takeaways from the Friday meeting (March 3rd 2026 8:40pm IST) directly relevant for the certification exam. 

1)  When you receive vouchers the expiry will mostly be in October 2026 not cumulative year.

2) The voucher  will be issued to utilize maximum only once per person. You need to pay if you don't utilize and want to have another attempt. 

3) Go to the Qiskit development certification website, through registration find out nearest ibm  centers and dates for this particular exam.


4)   Note: you can take it from home, but not even some of the default backgrounds programs should run else immediately disqualified voucher expires, (try to modify for all the requirements in separate guest account OS) , With web cam, should be shown the entire room and should  be clear  of any material ,if there are,  atleast should be unreachable and you cannot get up and move in the room or people come in. All these things will lead to automatic disqualification by default without further arbitration. The computer, you and the environment is constantly checked by Proctor in Tandem with AI software.

Take at home option is therefore very risky and tedious if not done properly. 

